      <h1>Accreditations</h1>
      <p>Arabian Drilling’s Training Center is proud to be recognized and accredited by leading industry organizations. Our accreditations demonstrate our commitment to delivering high-quality, internationally recognized training programs that meet rigorous standards for safety, technical excellence, and instructional quality.</p>
      <ul>
        <li>International Well Control Forum (IWCF) Accredited</li>
        <li>International Association of Drilling Contractors (IADC) Accredited</li>
        <li>Saudi Aramco Approved Training Provider</li>
        <li>General Organization for Technical and Vocational Training (TVTC) Certified</li>
        <li>ISO 9001:2015 Quality Management System</li>
      </ul>
      <p>These accreditations ensure our courses and certifications are recognized by employers and regulatory bodies worldwide, giving our trainees a competitive edge in the energy sector.</p>
